titles.title: Expressing the condolences of the House of Representatives on the death of the Honorable Juanita Millender-McDonald, a Representative from the State of California.

action.text: DEBATE - The House proceeded with one hour of debate on H. Res. 328.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 4/23/2007--Passed House without amendment. (This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.) Expresses the condolences of the House of Representatives on the death of the Honorable Juanita Millender-McDonald, a former Representative from California. Declares that when the House adjourns on April 23, 2007, it stand adjourned as a further mark of respect to the memory of Representative Millender-McDonald.
